title: HypolitaGivesInstructionsCombatTutorial
---
<<trigger_gesture ScientistHypolita LayingItAllOut>>
Hypolita: There's a Limacoid in the next chamber. You've seen earth slugs, no? This is like that but bigger and with more biting and spewing.
Hypolita: Be careful to avoid its bite and noxious spewing of contaminated gas.
<<trigger_gesture ScientistHypolita ShakeHead>>
